-- Buffett says he has bought more Wells Fargo shares
-- 
-- Wed Oct 24, 2012 8:26am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/10/24/us-berkshire-buffett-wells-idUSBRE89N0MP20121024

 

 (Reuters) - Berkshire Hathaway bought more shares of Wells Fargo bank over the last week amid broad market weakness, Chief Executive Warren Buffett said in a CNBC interview on Wednesday. 
 Wells Fargo is one of Berkshire's largest holdings. (Reporting By  Ben Berkowitz ; Editing by Maureen Bavdek)